quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  51,1,Ndahiriye ku miyaga ihuha igatatanya (ibicu)
  51,2,No ku bicu biremereye bitwara amazi (imvura)
  51,3,No ku mato agenda mu buryo bworoshye
  51,4,"No ku bamalayika bashinzwe gukwirakwiza (amafunguro, imvura n’indi migisha) ku bw’itegeko (rya Allah)"
  51,5,"Mu by’ukuri, ibyo musezeranywa (izuka n’ibindi bizaba ku munsi w’imperuka) ni impamo"
  51,6,"Kandi rwose, kuzagororerwa (cyangwa guhanwa ku bakoze ibibi) bizabaho nta kabuza"
  51,7,Ndahiriye ku kirere kirimo amayira ameze neza
  51,8,Rwose mufite imvugo zitandukanye (ku byerekeye intumwa Muhamadi ndetse n’iyi Quran)
  51,9,Uteshwa (gukurikira Quran n’intumwa Muhamadi) ni uwateshejwe (gukurikira ukuri)
  51,10,Abanyabinyoma baravumwe
  51,11,"Babandi bari mu bujiji, barangaye"
  51,12,Barabaza igihe umunsi w’ibihembo uzabera
  51,13,(Uzaba ari) umunsi bazaba bari mu muriro bahanwa
  51,14,"(Bazabwirwa bati) \"Ngaho nimusogongere ibihano byanyu; ibi ni byo mwajyaga musaba ko byihutishwa"
  51,15,"Mu by’ukuri, abatinya Allah bazaba bari mu busitani n’imigezi (mu Ijuru)"
  51,16,"Bishimisha mu byo Nyagasani wabo yabahaye. Mu by’ukuri, mbere bari abakora ibyiza"
  51,17,Bajyaga baryama gake mu ijoro (basenga Nyagasani wabo)
  51,18,No mu gicuku (wabasangaga) basaba imbabazi (Allah)
  51,19,"No mu mitungo yabo, bajyaga bagira icyo bageneramo abasabirizi n’abakene bihishira"
  51,20,No ku isi hari ibimenyetso ku bemera badashidikanya
  51,21,Ndetse no muri mwe ubwanyu (ibyo bimenyetso birimo). Ese ntimubona
  51,22,No mu kirere hari amafunguro yanyu ndetse n’ibyo musezeranywa
  51,23,"Bityo, ndahiriye ku izina rya Nyagasani w’ikirere n’isi ko (ibyo musezeranywa) ari ukuri nk’uko kuvuga kwanyu (ari ukuri)"